nodes.title: Positive
widgets_values:
A serene, dreamy scene unfolds against a soft, gradient lapis lazuli sky with layered, symmetrical clouds, and a thick white border, reminiscent of Hayao Miyazaki's whimsical style. A young, blonde-haired, small-breasted girl with pastel cyan eyes and multi-colored twin tails, adorned with hair ornaments, is shot from behind, her long, puffy sleeves and frilled skirt in dark black green hues, with a black bow and laced sleeves, evoking a sense of innocence. She stands amidst a sea of vibrant flowers, as light particles and shooting stars dance around her, imbuing the atmosphere with magic. The warm, golden light of a setting sun casts a gentle glow, with a subtle film grain and muted color grading, evoking a sense of nostalgia and wonder.
The painting is in the style of umesky. <lora:ume_sky_v2:1>
